3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper involves compositional learning algorithms and analysis of complexity gains, which are key topics in machine learning. 
4. cs.CL (Computation and Language) - The paper mentions a hierarchical dictionary of object parts, which could be related to natural language processing and language modeling. 
5. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The paper discusses the number of nodes (neurons) required for parallel processing, which is a topic in neural computing.
